        <detaileddescription>
<para>Used as the index into the sparse array of an EntityPool. Combined with a <ref refid="namespacehelios_1_1ecs_1_1types_1a58cc516088b7b594d813b712c9337c8a" kindref="member">VersionId</ref> in an <ref refid="structhelios_1_1ecs_1_1types_1_1EntityHandle" kindref="compound">EntityHandle</ref>, it enables safe entity references that detect stale handles after entity removal.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="structhelios_1_1ecs_1_1types_1_1EntityHandle" kindref="compound">EntityHandle</ref> </para>
